🚀 QUICK START COMMANDS

Backend:
  cd /backend
  python -m uvicorn api.main:app --reload --port 8000

Frontend:
  cd /frontend
  npm run dev

Browser:
  http://localhost:3000/register     (Create account)
  http://localhost:3000/login        (Sign in)
  http://localhost:3000/dashboard    (Main dashboard)

